cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.GT, cs.CR, cs.DC

The paper discusses the potential changes in the structure of the internet and the introduction of new indicators of quality of services, which are related to the fields of networking (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions game theoretical approaches (cs.GT) to net neutrality. Additionally, the paper discusses the need for regulation legislation and monitoring, which are related to the fields of cryptography (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
